{
  "2403550": {
    "name": "Where is My Son?",
    "steam_appid": 2403550,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/c77c141c9840b264beea4b5a934a7607.avif?t=1760637284\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>克里斯因妻子去世而深陷悲痛，当儿子也突然失踪时，他彻底崩溃了。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他寻找儿子塞德里克的旅程迅速演变成一场充满阴影、秘密和超自然力量的超现实冒险。奇怪的符号、被遗忘的地方和无法解释的事件开始浮出水面，将克里斯拖入一个逻辑崩溃、一切皆非表象的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>塞德里克为何失踪？他失踪背后隐藏着什么巨大秘密？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场充满爱、时间、黑暗与光明交织的戏剧性旅程，将揭开所有隐藏的真相。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索城镇、森林、医院、洞穴、房屋、迷宫、地下庇护所、隐藏区域、餐厅、商店等众多地点——与人物互动以发现线索并推进剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/9372a21891a91e0a3a9c2f5f6fda8f6a.poster.avif?t=1760637284\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/9372a21891a91e0a3a9c2f5f6fda8f6a.webm?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/9372a21891a91e0a3a9c2f5f6fda8f6a.mp4?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在探索洞穴时，你可能需要与熊战斗或打破岩石才能继续前进！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在寻找塞德里克的旅程中，请做好应对各种挑战的准备。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有时，你甚至需要将一条鱼带给餐厅老板才能获得线索！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/86e43fd8d3ef6ab8714846fea946aa57.poster.avif?t=1760637284\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/86e43fd8d3ef6ab8714846fea946aa57.webm?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/86e43fd8d3ef6ab8714846fea946aa57.mp4?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迷你游戏</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通过与某些物体互动，你可以触发一些非常有趣的场景！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时，你需要玩一款游戏机游戏或连接电线才能继续故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/12d40a79a3893ea95b17e3475b9c535a.poster.avif?t=1760637284\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/12d40a79a3893ea95b17e3475b9c535a.webm?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/12d40a79a3893ea95b17e3475b9c535a.mp4?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这还不是全部——更多惊喜迷你游戏将在整个故事中等待着你！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个戏剧性且令人惊喜的故事...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着克里斯寻找儿子塞德里克，过去与未来将以意想不到的方式交织，带来充满情感与感动的时刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/6742fdbcb0e76fb24580581d73f26979.poster.avif?t=1760637284\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/6742fdbcb0e76fb24580581d73f26979.webm?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/6742fdbcb0e76fb24580581d73f26979.mp4?t=1760637284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏开发者寄语：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色卡、11种语言选择、迷宫、 puzzles，以及我无法一一描述的更多特色内容，都将在这次冒险中等待着你。你甚至可能需要动手建造某些东西！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是一款游戏，对我来说，它就是生命本身。我们所有的悲伤、喜悦、梦想……简而言之，我们所经历的所有情感都在这款游戏中得以呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是这款游戏的创作者，Deniz Yukarıçukur。我也是一个父亲——一个3岁女儿的父亲——并且已婚。我尽力将生活中感受到的一切都融入了这款游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，我还加入了一些我们一直好奇但从未在现实生活中体验过的事物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望你们喜欢这款游戏。如果你们能将其加入愿望清单，帮助这个虽小却真诚的社区成长，我将非常高兴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403550/extras/9c5cc65d73b76eeda1a468f1a07aac2a.avif?t=1760637284\" width=616 height=212 /></span></p>",
